<%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
<title>About - Soundflow</title>
<%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>About Soundflow 🎶</h1>
      <p>Your gateway to discovering, enjoying, and curating the world’s music.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="about-page">
    <section class="about-intro">
      <p>
        Soundflow is your gateway to discovering, enjoying, and curating the world’s music.  
        From trending hits to hidden gems, we bring together the power of YouTube and MongoDB  
        to create a personalized music experience tailored just for you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <h2>✨ What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>🔥 <strong>Trending Music:</strong> See what’s hot right now across the globe.</li>
        <li>🔍 <strong>Smart Search:</strong> Find your favorite tracks, artists, or genres instantly.</li>
        <li>❤️ <strong>Favorites:</strong> Save and manage songs you love for quick access anytime.</li>
        <li>🎧 <strong>Seamless Listening:</strong> Watch, listen, and vibe with embedded YouTube players.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="vision">
      <h2>💡 Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        At Soundflow, we believe music is more than sound—it’s emotion, memory, and connection.  
        Our mission is to make music discovery effortless and enjoyable, whether you’re exploring  
        today’s top charts or revisiting timeless classics.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="future">
      <h2>🚀 What’s Next?</h2>
      <p>
        We’re continuously evolving—soon you’ll be able to create playlists, share music with friends,  
        and explore recommendations based on your taste. This is just the beginning of the Soundflow journey.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:20px;">
        Thank you for being a part of our growing community. Let’s keep the music flowing! 🎵
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-copy">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Soundflow. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
